{
  "id": "1-2",
  "title": "Act 2: The Unexpected Intruder",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch1_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 800,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "alert",
          "text": "[ Perimeter Shield Anomaly ── Breach Detected ]",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "instant"
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}}'s shelter was positioned dangerously close to the perimeter shield. So when the alarm sounded, it was as if it detonated right against her eardrums.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "A low-frequency wail emanated from the shield's edge. {{characters.alea.name}} sprang to her feet in the same instant.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This wasn't trained military instinct—it was the raw survival reflex honed over a decade on the lower decks.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "An alarm meant something from the wasteland had <em>gotten inside</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The shield had breached again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She tore a modified electromagnetic blade from the wall and kicked the door open, rushing into the corridor.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Outside was complete chaos. Residents bolted deeper into the corridor, clutching whatever possessions they could carry. Shrieks and frantic footsteps merged into a cacophony of panic.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} crouched low and moved <em>against the flow</em>, heading in the opposite direction.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Mutants tracked prey by vibration. Running toward crowds was a death wish.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "In the midst of the chaos, she caught an oddly distinct sound.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Not the broken sobs of despair or the roars of anger—",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "but a barely suppressed, trembling whisper.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "???",
          "text": "<whisper>Is... is anyone there?</whisper>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} stopped dead in her tracks.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She crouched at the corner of the hallway and peered into the clinic's main hall.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "In the dim light, a figure huddled behind a collapsed nurse's station, arms wrapped tightly around their knees. Blonde hair stood out starkly against the shadows.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "By their size, it was a child with an <em>Alpha body</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 500,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 6
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The next second, tremors through the floor pulled {{characters.alea.name}}'s nerves taut.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "A common wasteland mutant from the fringe—its exoskeleton fully chitinized, vision severely atrophied, was stalking the hall through vibrations alone.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 300,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Each dull footfall on the floor announced that it had moved <em>one step closer</em> to the child.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} grabbed a piece of metal scrap from the floor and hurled it at a window on the opposite side.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": "「Crash!」",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "instant"
          },
          "log": false
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The creature's attention snapped away. In the half-second it faltered, {{characters.alea.name}} charged into the hall, grabbed the child's wrist, and dragged her toward the side exit.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 400,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 8
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The mutant lunged. {{characters.alea.name}} spun and slashed with her blade—unable to pierce the creature's thick chitin, but the electromagnetic discharge found its mark at the joint of the hind leg, sending the beast stumbling.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Both of them crashed through the side door and tumbled into the back corridor.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} jammed herself against the door, gasping for breath.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She looked down at the child she'd pulled free.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The girl's blonde hair was a mess, covered in dust. Sensing {{characters.alea.name}}'s gaze, she looked up.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She <em>smiled</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Thank you. I'm <em>{{characters.lyra.name}}</em>. <delay ms=\"400\"/>What's your name?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} blinked.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "...{{characters.alea.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1000,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
